-DRAG AND DROP 
    to perform drag and drop ops
        Drag & drop library (like react-beautiful-dnd or dnd-kit).
        Store columns + tasks in state.
        Allow dragging tasks between columns.

        >> npm install @dnd-kit/core 
        @dnd-kit/core → base drag-and-drop functionality

        @dnd-kit/sortable → makes lists/columns sortable (great for Kanban)

        @dnd-kit/modifiers → optional helpers (like snapping, restricting movement, etc.)

-ANT
    If you mean Ant Design (AntD):

    It’s a React-based UI framework built by Alibaba.

    Provides ready-to-use components like buttons, forms, tables, modals, layouts, etc.

    Has a clean, enterprise-style design system.

    Often used with React projects to speed up frontend development

    >>npm i ant

